earncpp.com\/cpp-tutorial\/arithmetic-conversions\/\">10.5 -- Arithmetic conversions<\/a><\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-text\">Added section: std::common_type and std::common_type_t<\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"changetable-row\"><div class=\"changetable-group-1\"><span class=\"changetable-row-date\">2024 Sep 20<\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-action\">Revision<\/span><\/div><div class=\"changetable-group-2\"><span class=\"changetable-row-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.learncpp.com\/cpp-tutorial\/type-deduction-for-objects-using-the-auto-keyword\/\">10.8 -- Type deduction for objects using the auto keyword<\/a><\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-text\">Clarified some type deduction cases with const and constexpr<\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"changetable-row\"><div class=\"changetable-group-1\"><span class=\"changetable-row-date\">2024 Sep 20<\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-action\">Revision<\/span><\/div><div class=\"changetable-group-2\"><span class=\"changetable-row-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.learncpp.com\/cpp-tutorial\/constant-variables-named-constants\/\">5.1 -- Constant variables (named constants)<\/a><\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-text\">Clarified that const is part of the type of an object<\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"changetable-row\"><div class=\"changetable-group-1\"><span class=\"changetable-row-date\">2024 Sep 17<\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-action\">Revision<\/span><\/div><div class=\"changetable-group-2\"><span class=\"changetable-row-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.learncpp.com\/cpp-tutorial\/constant-variables-named-constants\/\">5.1 -- Constant variables (named constants)<\/a><\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-text\">Added section: Why variables should be made constant<\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"changetable-row\"><div class=\"changetable-group-1\"><span class=\"changetable-row-date\">2024 Sep 13<\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-action\">Revision<\/span><\/div><div class=\"changetable-g