- Variable assignment and initialization<\/a><\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-text\">Corrected definition of initializer (vs initial value)<\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"changetable-row\"><div class=\"changetable-group-1\"><span class=\"changetable-row-date\">2024 Feb 15<\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-action\">Revision<\/span><\/div><div class=\"changetable-group-2\"><span class=\"changetable-row-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.learncpp.com\/cpp-tutorial\/configuring-your-compiler-choosing-a-language-standard\/\">0.12 -- Configuring your compiler: Choosing a language standard<\/a><\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-text\">Added notes about experimental\/preview build support<\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"changetable-row\"><div class=\"changetable-group-1\"><span class=\"changetable-row-date\">2024 Feb 2<\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-action\">Revision<\/span><\/div><div class=\"changetable-group-2\"><span class=\"changetable-row-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.learncpp.com\/cpp-tutorial\/user-defined-namespaces-and-the-scope-resolution-operator\/\">7.2 -- User-defined namespaces and the scope resolution operator<\/a><\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-text\">Added section: How to use namespaces<\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"changetable-row\"><div class=\"changetable-group-1\"><span class=\"changetable-row-date\">2024 Jan 28<\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-action\">Revision<\/span><\/div><div class=\"changetable-group-2\"><span class=\"changetable-row-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.learncpp.com\/cpp-tutorial\/struct-miscellany\/\">13.11 -- Struct miscellany<\/a><\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-text\">Added tip about minimizing padding<\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"changetable-row\"><div class=\"changetable-group-1\"><span class=\"changetable-row-date\">2024 Jan 26<\/span><span class=\"changetable-row-action\">Revision<\/span><\/div><div class=\"changetable-group-2\"><span class=\"changetable-row-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/